OL,3,CDriver arrested following serious
OL,4,Ccollision in Cumbria
OL,6,FA driver has been arrested following a
OL,7,F'serious' road collision near Kendal.
OL,9,FEmergency services responded to
OL,10,Freports of the collision on the A591,
OL,11,Fwhich involved a car and a motorbike,
OL,12,Fat around 6:40am.
OL,14,FThe motorbike rider was taken to
OL,15,Fhospital with serious injuries.
OL,17,FPolice say the driver of the car was
OL,18,Farrested on suspicion of causing
OL,19,Fserious injury by driving without due
OL,20,Fcare and attention, and a positive
OL,21,Fdrugs wipe.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
