OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1779901593
OL,3,CDriver arrested following serious
OL,4,Ccollision in Cumbria
OL,6,FThe A591 north from Brettargh Holt was
OL,7,Fclosed for several hours but has since
OL,8,Freopened.
OL,10,FThe closure also included the
OL,11,Fadjoining Whetstone Lane - and
OL,12,Fsouthbound traffic travelling towards
OL,13,FBrettargh or M6 junction 36 was
OL,14,Freduced to one lane.
OL,16,FPolice urged people to avoid the area,
OL,17,Fas the disruption affected people
OL,18,Ftravelling in and out of the Lake
OL,19,FDistrict from the M6.
